						<summary>

						<p>Pillar in the courtyard, Saṅgamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1. • • • ., Pushya ba. • • • makara-sankrānti, Wednesday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers an endowment for burning lamps in the temple of Chōḍēśvara-mahādēva at Chēbrōlu by Ko[ṭa]-bōyaṇḍu, Komana-bōyandu and Kōṭana-bōyaṇḍu, sons of Boṁ[ḍikōṭa] Eṛaya-seṭṭi.</p>						

